title: Motorcycle acrobatics and flying man delight crowds at India's 'Rural Olympics'
text:
Motorcycle acrobatics and flying man delight crowds at India's 'Rural Olympics' 4:03pm IST - 01:05 
A three-day sporting spectacle in India's northern Punjab region attracts thousands of people eager to show off some of their rather unusual skills.
